    "setup_phase": "Step 1: Open a Direct Mutual Fund account on Groww, Kuvera, or Coin (these apps charge 0 like Zerodha). You'll need PAN, Aadhar, and bank details. Step 2: Lumpsum invest ₹2,800,000 as follows: ₹14L HDFC Flexi Cap (35%), ₹8L ICICI Prudential Large & Mid (20%), ₹6L Motilal Oswal Midcap (15%), ₹3.2L UTI Gold ETF (8%), ₹480K Motilal Oswal S&P 500 (12%). Step 3: Start 4 SIPs monthly: ₹52,500 HDFC Flexi Cap (35%), ₹30,000 ICICI Large & Mid (20%), ₹22,500 Motilal Midcap (15%), ₹12,000 UTI Gold (8%), ₹18,000 Motilal S&P 500 (12%). Verify first SIP in 5 days. Step 4: Set reminder to check portfolio value on Jan 1st every year (not monthly!).",
    "review_checkpoints": [
      "Month 1: Verify all 5 SIPs are running correctly. Check statement NAVs match expected ~1L NAV for equities."
