    "rebalancing_guidelines": "Rebalance once a year on Jan 1st. If any category drifts more than 5% from target (e.g., Gold dips to 6% or US rises to 14%), sell the excess and buy the deficit. Don't rebalance less than 5% unless market crash happens (use global ETF for immediate firepower).",
